main event: Three luminous objects were observed moving from east to west for a duration of 20-30 seconds.
interesting points: The objects were described as light blue and hazy., One object moved up and down while others remained stationary., The lights in the area went out during the sighting., The observation was made visually without any optical aids., The sighting occurred at night.
sighted object: three luminous objects in the sky
witness description: A housewife and two teachers from Canon, New Mexico.
